  %body#page-top{"data-spy" => "scroll", "data-target" => ".navbar-custom"}
    %nav.navbar.navbar-custom.navbar-fixed-top{:role => "navigation"}
      .container
        .navbar-header.page-scroll
          %button.navbar-toggle{"data-target" => ".navbar-main-collapse", "data-toggle" => "collapse", :type => "button"}
            %i.fa.fa-bars
          %a.navbar-brand{:href => "#page-top"}
            %i.fa.fa-play-circle
            %span.light
              Llewellyn Radford
        / Collect the nav links, forms, and other content for toggling
        .collapse.navbar-collapse.navbar-right.navbar-main-collapse
          %ul.nav.navbar-nav
            / Hidden li included to remove active class from about link when scrolled up past about section
            %li.hidden
              %a{:href => "#page-top"}
            %li.page-scroll
              %a{:href => "#about"} About
            %li.page-scroll
              %a{:href => "#download"} Projects
            %li.page-scroll
              %a{:href => "#contact"} Contact
        / /.navbar-collapse
      / /.container
    %section.intro
      .intro-body
        .container
          .row
            .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
              %h1.brand-heading Llewellyn Radford
              %p.intro-text "Dream on Dreamers"
              .page-scroll
                %a.btn.btn-circle{:href => "#about"}
                  %i.fa.fa-angle-double-down.animated
    %section#about.container.content-section.text-center
      .row
        .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
          %h2 About Llewellyn
          %p
            Born in Bartow, Florida and raised in Newport News, Virginia. Llewellyn C. Radford II broke into the entertainment industry as a model while attending Hampton University. Pushed by his mother to attend an open casting call, Llewellyn gained his first acting experience as a background actor on the $30 Million Warner Bros picture
            %a{:href => "http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0362478/"} The Box
            starring Cameron Diaz, James Marsden, and Frank Langella. The experience allowed him to discover his passion for acting.
          %p
            While on a spontaneous trip to Chicago for the 4th of July in 2008 he cheated on modeling with acting and has never looked back. In October 2009, he stepped out on faith and decided to move to Los Angeles, California when his close friend
            %a{:href => "http://weknowthedj.com/"} DJ Tay James
            was hired as Justin Bieber's official DJ. He landed at LAX with $500 and a single bag.  .
          %p The past five years have been an incredible journey for Llewellyn. In that time he has been involved in numerous creative projects from acting, song writing, and spoken word poetry. To this day Llewellyn continues to chase his dreams and lives to inspire others every step of the way.
    %section#download.content-section.text-center
      .download-section
        .container
          .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
            %h2 Projects
            %p
              Past, current, and future projects that Llwelleyn has been a part of will be published here and linked to. In the meantime please check out Llewellyns
              %a{:href => "http://weknowthedj.com/"} YouTube Channel
              where he consistently updates his reel and posts shorts.
            %a.btn.btn-default.btn-lg{:href => "http://imdb.com"} Visit LLwellyns IMDB Page
    %section#contact.container.content-section.text-center
      .row
        .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
          %h2 Contact Llwellyn
          %p For inquiries or booking please email Llewellyn. You can also follow him on social media. Dream on Dreamers!
          %p llwellynradford@gmail.com
          %ul.list-inline.banner-social-buttons
            %li
              %a.btn.btn-default.btn-lg{:href => "https://twitter.com/hollywoodlue"}
                %i.fa.fa-twitter.fa-fw
                %span.network-name Twitter
            %li
              %a.btn.btn-default.btn-lg{:href => "https://instagram.com/hollywoodlue"}
                %i.fa.fa-instagram.fa-fw
                %span.network-name Instagram
            %li
              %a.btn.btn-default.btn-lg{:href => "https://facebook.com/"}
                %i.fa.fa-facebook.fa-fw
                %span.network-name Facebook+
